OL,4,CSex Pistols in legal dispute over Danny
OL,5,CBoyle's new TV series
OL,6, A legal battle between three former
OL,7, members of the Sex Pistols has begun in
OL,8, the High Court in London.
OL,10,FGuitarist Steve Jones and drummer Paul
OL,11,FCook are suing frontman John Lydon to
OL,12,Fallow the use of their songs in a new
OL,13,FDanny Boyle-directed TV series, Pistol.
OL,15,FThe show, which is being made by
OL,16,FDisney, is based on Jones's memoir.
OL,18,FBut Lydon - aka Johnny Rotten - has
OL,19,Fsaid he is not prepared to approve the
OL,20,Fnecessary licences for the punk band's
OL,21,Fmusic unless ordered to by a court.
